      "id": "33",
      "name": "Gallery",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "id": "gallery_character53139",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/14/88913591/c2868aeb5ca6327bb10f99c79970aa22_6314024096387542834.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Find <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">challengers in the open world</span> or enter the tavern after reaching Player Level 2 to play matches against <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">weekly visiting</span> challengers and earn Player EXP, which will increase your Player Level. As your Player Level increases, you will unlock new functions and matches. Upon reaching a certain Player Level, you can also challenge Prince in Ascension Challenges to further elevate your maximum level capacity.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/5"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character81361",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/14/88913591/bb0c3bbd1166b98abaf01141d44ed267_1785402334667582368.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Genius Invokation is a popular card game with <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">players coming from all corners of the world</span>. Face them in matches and overcome them to get <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">P</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">layer EXP and Lucky Coins</span>. Should you be fortunate, some rivals might even gift you certain cards as a parting gift after the culmination of your duel. As your Player Level increases, the number of challengers you can face and the matches you can partake in will also increase…</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/5"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character47118",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/14/88913591/d597346abb50c24691738a064c011cec_7093326357954392803.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>You can use the <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">invitation board</span> to send invitations to registered challengers and partake in matches. Should you prevail in these matches, you can also earn corresponding <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Character and Talent Cards</span>.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/5"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character79334",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/14/88913591/25342b3e238e883ae1d4eea8b6240f10_227811221038142203.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>You can use the invitation board and connect with your friends via Co-Op to engage in matchmaking. As your Player Level grows, you can also challenge faraway strangers to duels of skill.</p>",
                "key": "Page 4/5"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character75714",
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/14/88913591/d92e65db154e2ee58c42c7432e9e18c7_656169617745875248.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Spend the Lucky Coins you earn from Genius Invokation TCG matches at The Cat's Tail. You can use Lucky Coins to purchase <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">cards, cards backs, and dynamic skins</span>, amongst other items.</p>",
                "key": "Page 5/5"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
